Kuwait Seeks to Set New Rules for Investment Firms, Reuters Says

-- B y   F i o n a   M a c D o n a l d
-- 
2011-05-30T14:32:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/kuwait-seeks-to-set-new-rules-for-investment-firms-reuters-says.html
Kuwaiti investment firms will need
separate licenses to operate lending and investment businesses,
Reuters reported, citing a central bank circular.  Investment firms have one month to decide on the licenses
and the circular was sent last week, according to the news
agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fiona MacDonald in Kuwait at 
 fmacdonald4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
